    "However, when disagreements in the coding of responses arose, the second author suggested renaming the codes or adding a new code.",
    "When the two coders disagreed, the third author was asked to also code the disputed coding.",
    "Inter-coder reliability between the first and second authors was computed using percent agreement.",
    "The average percent agreement across the two datasets is 97%, which is very high.",
    "However, 100% percent agreement was achieved during the consensus discussions involving all three coders."
